org.yamcs.http.websocket

Interface WebSocketResource

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlarmResource, CommandHistoryResource, CommandQueueResource, EventResource, InstanceResource, LinkResource, ManagementResource, PacketResource, ParameterResource, ProcessorResource, StreamResource, StreamsResource, TimeResource

    public interface WebSocketResource
    A resource bundles a set of logically related operations. Instances are created for every client session separately.
